The '''1891 [[VMI Keydets]] football team''' represented the [[Virginia Military Institute]] in their first ever season of organized football. In 1871, however, VMI played [[Washington and Lee University]] in a one-game season, losing 4-2. No coaching or player records are known from that game.<ref>[http://www.cfbdatawarehouse.com/data/div_iaa/bigsouth/virginia_military_institute/yearly_results.php?year=1873 Virginia Military Institute Game by Game Results<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref>
